{"tid":1557001,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪應該整合一個良心小店同罷食app等大家方便唔好去錯","createTime":"2019-09-10T03:00:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T04:02:04.000Z","uid":90341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3282685d63b5f0f6512dc52a984bb7f8b95197db","tid":1557001,"uid":90341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:00:49.000Z","msg":"發聲小店好需要大家支持，而家淨係靠文宣好似作用唔夠大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4f0fc86d419328c1358a7000c153e43ee91f8f","tid":1557001,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:14:29.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n手足每晚都好努力貼連儂，凌晨3-6就比人清！<br />\n913 914 915 活動要去，但請起返連儂牆<br />\n<ins>考驗毅力與堅持</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">做更具價值嘅野</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">等所有人知道發生緊咩事先！</span></span></strong><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">連儂牆起源於反共，呢條戰線不能倒！</code></pre><br />\n勇武走得太前，做人要有公關！<br />\n文宣多一個就好多！連儂牆要人！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一場抗爭/革命搞十年八載唔出奇<br />\n<strong>衛城革命，生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</strong><br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n0. <span style=\"color: red;\">幫襯</span>良心小店<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">抵制</span>「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全之下，<span style=\"color: red;\">免費港鐵</span>；二人同遊，一人免費<br />\n3. 夜晚<span style=\"color: red;\">十點吶喊</span>！！！連繫左鄰右里<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: red;\">每日一post</span>，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD63e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=18b0c152\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span>，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">低消費</span>，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">做孝子救港</span>，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span>貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF都買美股<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會事務，做陪審員、派傳單、放映會<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.09"},{"pid":"624310a0accaa30c044a32f5d8720a221ab7d900","tid":1557001,"uid":143580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:25:49.000Z","msg":"前排有巴打整咗個app㗎！要揾揾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ntg琴晚見到有個bot from 老豆揾仔<br />\n<br />\n希望大家消費罷買前都查一查先<br />\n唔會晒好多時間 黃店藍店都查到 會定期更新<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ybshopbot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fybshopbot&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD63e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=b528a428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ybshopbot</a>"},{"pid":"82fe7c45b22eb226e53948bfcd4746a18f61e1ea","tid":1557001,"uid":143580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:31:46.000Z","msg":"幫襯藍絲，不了! 全力支持真香港人食肆bot 上線啦!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1557006\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1557006</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"865db60ff7606fe54150efe195a2f49c701d0b6f","tid":1557001,"uid":97863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"624310a0accaa30c044a32f5d8720a221ab7d900","tid":1557001,"uid":143580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:25:49.000Z","msg":"前排有巴打整咗個app㗎！要揾揾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ntg琴晚見到有個bot from 老豆揾仔<br />\n<br />\n希望大家消費罷買前都查一查先<br />\n唔會晒好多時間 黃店藍店都查到 會定期更新<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ybshopbot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fybshopbot&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD63e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=b528a428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ybshopbot</a>"},"citedBy":0,"r